---
alwaysApply: true
description: Global rule to strictly enforce LSP usage instead of text search/grep
globs: *
---
When exploring the codebase to understand symbols, functions, or classes, strictly prioritize using Language Server (LSP) features (like Go to Definition, Find All References, and Document Symbols). 

Do NOT use raw text search (like `grep` or `rg`) unless semantic tools fail or you are explicitly asked to look for specific hardcoded strings.